Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.92,0:01:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候起  我就时常能看到奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是被称作是妖怪一类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你往哪踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  危险  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  那边是别人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  麻烦你捡下球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球  球…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张脸  是夏目大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐在你身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  这绳子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来以前好像也有过这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐交出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐  快交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被妖怪缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事干就跟着来了  你就这德行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老师  很难受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶  蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帐交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我…  很难受啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是干什么吧  蠢猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你说过我不是猫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以招财猫为凭依的暂时的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你是保镖吧  那就认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别把我当普通保镖使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了得到友人帐而在等你寿命终结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用重新解释  你这大福饼猫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  总有一天我要吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
