Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收留了无处可去  在亲戚间被推来推去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心地善良的藤原夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵志  吃饭啰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵吉还没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它没来吃饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在外面吃过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了它就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个好吃  是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百合根啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不给他们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看见妖怪的事绝对要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没回房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我打得太用力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫  猫咪老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我啊  你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了  老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿你的脏爪子到处踩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干了什么啊  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我刚才打了你  闹别扭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.49,0:05:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  刚才是老师你不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只黑的是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这家伙是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  不是老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目了然吧  呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸盘这么大的猫没几只吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这家伙是变成老师的样子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  友人帐没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  跑哪去了  那只黑猫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  这么黑可找不到那黑家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  友人帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人类晚上在外面晃很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今晚的空气好像跟平常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一会  再让我找一会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上面有妖怪们重要的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:06:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻滚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  冷静下来夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然友人帐被抢很让人生气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我感觉那只黑猫没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在吵吵闹闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让别的妖怪知道友人帐被抢了会更麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量不少啊  这是要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像闻到  有人类的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老 老师  好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一忍  用我的味道掩盖过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想着是不是人  这是野兽的腥臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说是腥臭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么高贵而伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  以前主人经常带着人的味道回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人化成人的样子去村里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带些好吃的回来分给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的人类  跟他们扯上关系就没好下场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是斑大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您这身姿何时看都是这么美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你是红峰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您正在用餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那请务必分我一点残羹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这张脸好像在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目玲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子  声音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是夏目玲子的孙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰  刚才那群妖怪是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是森林里的妖怪聚集起来开宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  你在这附近见过一只叼着一叠纸的可爱黑猫没
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  倒是有只大头肥猫往宴会场去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…肥猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰小姐  能带我们去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的吗  人类的孩子去了立刻就会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就装成妖怪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  我必须得找到那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这任性的眼神  的确是像玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是喜欢他这点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊  再废话就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我就带你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能顺利装成妖怪也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到时候你被认出来是人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当大家的下酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！斑大人变成豆丁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒是在这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又不是去喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  夏目少爷得化妆或是戴面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人也不能露出野兽的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟您很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目玲子把友人帐传给了长得像她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着野兽的少年这事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到处都在传的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你想让那孩子在家待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  哥哥也说他不愿意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你回来啦  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  找到玲子阿姨的遗物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的祖母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这是什么  涂鸦本？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她是个怪人  看来相当怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个扔掉也可以哦  贵志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西留着也没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生拥有强大妖力的祖母玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将打败的妖怪的名字写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订立了主从契约
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我一点都不知道友人帐和玲子祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人就以这副样子去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  红峰  来得真迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不解风情  我化了个妆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  没见过的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩啊  也让我们加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  来来  喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我说你  有点人类的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我想起主人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  主人也老是带着人类的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢人类的森林之主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他变成人的样子去村里玩的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到捕狐狸的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从被一个猎人救了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就经常变成人去见那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还为交到了人类朋友而雀跃不已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那位大人妖力虽然强大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑却不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会想和人类交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  还跟那个夏目玲子比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  有谁在附近看到一只黑猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多来谈谈那件事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到可恶人类封印主人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是复仇的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人将力量分给下等的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让我们住在这森林里的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  我们就进行夜袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类根本不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起进攻他们就不堪一击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜袭是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人袭击了家畜  所以被人类封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是终于找到封印地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那个高高的红墙房子的地板下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.11,0:13:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也没必要袭击那房子里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没必要  不过看这些家伙喝成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知会做出什么事来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你  可别去多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个数量是无法轻易阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  你就别管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正人类能做到的事也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还好  我能听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能听到他们的声音  还有人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分厚薄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就一点忙也帮不上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟玲子不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子真难懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底喜欢他哪一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感兴趣的是友人帐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶紧把他吃掉  抢过来不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也能给我杀杀时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.71,0:15:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生很短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到它了  老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  这家伙怎么这么老实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只黑猫会不会是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得它是想通过抢友人帐  把我们带到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰  你办得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感应一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是强大的妖怪被封印在某个凭依上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭依啊  这样做很流行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这妖气… 很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难道是主人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怜了  可恶的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印了却还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高的红墙房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候弄断的绳子是这只黑猫的结界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰小姐  赶快通知大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人这个样子  谁都不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把封印解开  恢复以前的样子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有个低级妖怪说这家伙跟玲子比赛过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  听说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个  或许是因为名字被夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它才无法打破封印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把名字还给它的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过问题在于名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装在凭依里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:17:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帐是不会自动搜索名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红峰小姐  主人的名字叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  我也只知道叫他主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我一定会把名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你帮忙阻止大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个  在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发  是要去袭击人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人已经回到这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  呆子  别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁知道主人的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道了名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.67,0:17:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人类的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  该死的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  滚一边去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意听  这其中应该会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会有知道主人名字的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追  我把名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主…人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你而能活动了的我  去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生真短暂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点明白为什么大家会说我笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会抢友人帐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到森林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪们正想为我去袭击人类的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有力量阻止  就把你带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你应该能做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印你的也是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却想要阻止妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不会再到人类的村子里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  人类的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了啊  黑猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑猫咪真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:21:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你以为是靠了谁这次的事件才能解决的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  斑大人的伤也不碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.81,0:21:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是无法喜欢人类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想着为了斑大人  就找机会把你给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却碍于主人的大恩不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人  要不干脆就跟我一起回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我还是暂时待在这家伙身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一眨眼的功夫过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  猫咪老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坦率起来还真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的烦恼是  小小的离别带来的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间的邂逅与分别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一个一个的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好珍惜起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:50.91,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}融化在春天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是芝原野的石像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.33,0:23:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是有两座的  还有一座怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…  她已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

